<div class="taxonomy-term-description">ACellShop  uses only the highest grade 3M vinyl for our Razer Blade Stealth skins. What does that mean? Most importantly, it’s a guarantee that your new Blade Stealth skin uses the most textured, premium material on the planet. Furthermore, it means that when you’re ready to remove your Razer Blade Stealth wrap and replace it with a fresh one, we guarantee it’ll leave no adhesive residue or damage to your device. By committing to exclusive use of 3M vinyl, we’re confidently able to stand behind our bold claims.</div></div>
