    Our Variety, Your Choice  </h3>
<div class="taxonomy-term-description">We’re constantly adding new textures and materials to our portfolio of Razer Blade Stealth decals. Right now, we offer Blade Stealth skins in a variety of finishes such as Zebra Wood, Mahogany, Carbon Fiber, Leather, True Colour, and Matte. Our one of a kind customization interface allows you to get a true preview of exactly how your Razer Blade Stealth is going to look with a wrap on it. You can even mix and match the top, bottom, and trackpad at no additional cost. Also, because you were probably wondering, no: the trackpad skin doesn't affect the trackpad sensitivity whatsoever.</div></div>
